node.text:
The new BUGATTI smartwatch range, created with VIITA Watches, mirrors the unrivalled precision, artistry and technology synonymous with hyper sports cars crafted in Molsheim. Each of the models offers an innumerable amount of technical features and is built by hand with meticulous attention to detail for a seamless integration of more than 1,000 individual parts. Discover the collection at www.bugatti.com or www.bugatti-smartwatches.com. @bugatti_smartwatches

#BUGATTI #BUGATTILifestyle #BUGATTISmartwatches #VIITA #VIITAforBUGATTI #VIITAWatches

node.text: No other driver spends more time in a BUGATTI CHIRON than he does: Andy Wallace. In the last few years, the Englishman and Pilote Officiel covered a total of over 150,000 km in the hyper sports cars from Molsheim. He thus is the perfect person to show owners and fans how to make the most of this unique vehicle. In a series of five video clips, Andy explains the car’s technical details in a comprehensible manner and reveals what the CHIRON is capable of and still driving it safely. Fasten your seatbelts! #BUGATTI #Chiron #AndyWallace

node.text: No other driver spends more time in a BUGATTI CHIRON than he does: Andy Wallace. Fasten your seatbelts! #BUGATTI #Chiron #AndyWallace

The @jacobandco Bugatti Chiron Sapphire Crystal is the result of two years of research and development, and several months of materials processing, high level machining and hand polishing to produce a case with an unparalleled view of the 578 hand-decorated and hand-assembled components of the exclusive JCAM37 manual wound caliber. Sapphire is one of the hardest natural materials in the world, only eclipsed by diamond. Because of this diamond-tools are required to craft the case. Polishing is the most difficult and time consuming process taking a craftsman approximately 120 hours to complete the case by hand. This same delicate hand polishing is used for the caseback, the top, the three crowns and other pieces that are attached to the case. The result is a unique piece that fully exposes the groundbreaking totally functional replica of the BUGATTI W16 engine with its pistons pumping, turbochargers spinning as well as the whirl of the one-minute tourbillon.

#BUGATTI #BUGATTIChiron #JacobandCo #JacobandCoWatches #hautehorlogerie

Over the past weekend, BUGATTI’s long-standing UK dealer partner @hrowen was showcasing our marque’s latest masterpiece at @salonpriveuk, the CHIRON Super Sport - BUGATTI’s ultimate Grand Tourisme.

BUGATTI’s presence at the world-renowned event has been complemented by the @Jacobandco Twin Turbo Furious Bugatti, a grand complication movement made up of 832 individual parts, and the Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon in Rose Gold with diamonds, a unique piece that fully exposes the groundbreaking totally functional replica of the BUGATTI W16 engine with its pistons pumping, turbochargers spinning as well as the whirl of the one-minute tourbillon.

As exceptional creators of the smallest BUGATTI currently available to purchase, @little.cars joined the presentation with two of their highly exclusive Baby Bugatti II, an Italian Red Vitesse and a French Racing Blue Pur Sang, both models featuring the high performance power train utilising a 2.8 kWh battery and the 10kW high speed mode, accessible by using the ‘Speed Key’.

⁠⁠#BUGATTI #BUGATTIChiron #ChironSuperSport #SalonPrive #SalonPrive2021 #LittleCarCompany #JacobandCo #BlenheimPalace

After making its North American debut at Monterey Car Week on the West Coast last month, BUGATTI’s ultimate Grand Tourisme, the CHIRON Super Sport, has now reached the American East Coast to continue its US tour ready to conquer Manhattan.

#BUGATTI #BUGATTIChiron #CHIRON #CHIRONSuperSport #ManhattanMotorcars #NewYorkCity
–
This model is not subject to Directive 1999/94/EC, as it is a technical concept.

Our ferocious titan of speed has reached the East Coast of the United States.

BUGATTI’s latest hyper sports car, the CHIRON Super Sport, defined by its streamlined longtail bodywork, joins a long line of Super Sport ancestors as the ultimate Grand Tourisme. 

1,600 PS delivers brutal performance, yet encapsulates occupants in total comfort at speeds over 400 km/h.

#BUGATTI #BUGATTIChiron #CHIRON #CHIRONSuperSport

node.text:
BUGATTI prides itself in the relentless pursuit of engineering perfection, and has continued to do so for more than 110 years. The extreme testing and development process that the CENTODIECI has been subject to is part of achieving this goal. 
 
Subject to hurricane-force winds, the airflow generated inside the wind tunnel envelopes the hyper sports car’s intricate bodywork, so that it can be fine-tuned for optimum aerodynamic performance.
 
Just 10 units of the highly exclusive CENTODIECI will ever be crafted at our Atelier in Molsheim, with deliveries set to begin next year.

#BUGATTI #BUGATTICentodieci #CENTODIECI 
_
This model is not subject to Directive 1999/94/EC, as type approval has not yet been granted.

Behind the aerodynamic scenes of BUGATTI’s extensive testing program. 

Even as a few-off model, the CENTODIECI’s bodywork is fine-tuned to absolute perfection to achieve optimum aerodynamic performance.

#BUGATTI #CENTODIECI

node.text:
The unmistakable and timeless BUGATTI horseshoe grill, yet this time, it adorns the most provocative bodywork ever designed and fitted to one of our masterpieces. 

The BOLIDE is tailored to outperform. With its ultra-lightweight construction, thoroughbred DNA and eye-watering performance, the BOLIDE is the ultimate BUGATTI driving experience.

#BUGATTI #BUGATTIBolide #BOLIDE 
–
This model is not subject to Directive 1999/94/EC, as it is a technical concept.

Traversing the French Riviera on your way to Saint-Tropez is incredible enough, but using a CHIRON Sport and Pur Sport to complete the journey takes everything to the next level.

Each is designed to master the road beneath, taking dynamic turns and sweeps in their stride. 

#BUGATTI #BUGATTIChiron #CHIRON #CHIRONPurSport #CHIRONSport
